{"tid":1758712,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會正副主席","createTime":"2019-11-27T08:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:53:02.000Z","uid":184801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09813efe47b255586649529dc93608ad7903bd81","tid":1758712,"uid":184801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"各區區議會除左大會<br />\n仲有好多小組<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n九龍城區議會工作小組<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/meetings/working_group/workgroup_meetings.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkc%2Ftc_chi%2Fmeetings%2Fworking_group%2Fworkgroup_meetings.php&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=e983145c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/meetings/working_group/workgroup_meetings.php</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘區議會工作小組<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/meetings/working_group/workgroup_meetings.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkt%2Ftc_chi%2Fmeetings%2Fworking_group%2Fworkgroup_meetings.php&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=eaaaee22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kt/tc_chi/meetings/working_group/workgroup_meetings.php</a><br />\n<br />\n我地應該俾壓力各個候任區議員<br />\n除左大會正副主席<br />\n工作小組既正副主席都要係泛民既人<br />\n唔可以俾建制有任何機會上下其手！"},{"pid":"05fa8c57225d35a7a574a97db2643ca2c7912ba8","tid":1758712,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vq2VS6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq2VS6P.jpg&h=df2259db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKP5vTv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKP5vTv.jpg&h=24d6f0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"054d6a610b9f372152111f4035572c83535de2de","tid":1758712,"uid":266755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"f6d586c75e6789a3914e4676a1f0d99081d06c9d","tid":1758712,"uid":278765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"千祈咪畀隻鯨閪做正/副煮直，否則前功盡廢"},{"pid":"3621a60827688515a789e1c0f13a282f20dbd5a5","tid":1758712,"uid":71233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"推, 唔好畀泛民暗地裏同政府/共狗講數"},{"pid":"361de6f62ce53f2cc4bc38b9336d9a9328946322","tid":1758712,"uid":332362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實區議會係唯ㄧ擁有絶對認受性 可把整個平台推到高過垃圾會。"},{"pid":"d487d80fa0f82e9e62c602ec6a42025ca929f384","tid":1758712,"uid":184801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3621a60827688515a789e1c0f13a282f20dbd5a5","tid":1758712,"uid":71233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"推, 唔好畀泛民暗地裏同政府/共狗講數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"Yes<br />\n俾D機會新議員<br />\n唔可以俾任何位建制議員"},{"pid":"cc0db0e7fe5be8b8aff6dc16c40e2557ff5c3d45","tid":1758712,"uid":278311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"借各位推一推<br />\n〈策略POST〉老手新手區議員互相合作，共享「經驗」同「資源」，建立居民既「政治意識」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1758750/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1758750/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"72da3ef83bc8d9fd11e57776a8f5f0c6254325c0","tid":1758712,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"全部要霸哂, 要親中少數派無定企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536364cc185c02f74d06